import React, { useState } from "react"; import "./App.css"; import { MDBContainer, MDBNavbar, MDBNavbarBrand, MDBNavbarToggler, MDBIcon, MDBNavbarNav, MDBNavbarItem, MDBNavbarLink, MDBBtn, MDBDropdown, MDBDropdownToggle, MDBDropdownMenu, MDBDropdownItem, MDBDropdownLink, MDBCollapse, } from "mdb-react-ui-kit"; import logo1 from "./img/logo1.png"; function MainNav() { const [showBasic, setShowBasic] = useState(false); function resizeHeaderOnScroll() { const distanceY = window.pageYOffset || document.documentElement.scrollTop, shrinkOn = 5, headerEl = document.getElementById('navbar'); if (distanceY > shrinkOn) { headerEl.classList.add("smaller"); } else { headerEl.classList.remove("smaller"); } } window.addEventListener('scroll', resizeHeaderOnScroll); window.addEventListener("load", transNav) window.addEventListener("scroll", transNav) let navbar = document.getElementById("navbar") let scrollElement = document.getElementById("scrollElement") function transNav() { if (scrollElement.getBoundingClientRect(navbar).top <= 620) { navbar.style.background = "white" } else { navbar.style.background = "transparent" } } return ( setShowBasic(!showBasic)} > Home All Properties Agents Agent John Ryan Agent Kevin Richmond Agent Mary Williams Contact Us
